How to update U-Boot from running OS
====================================

#. Install u-boot-mcom02-firmware-tools package.

#. Choose U-Boot image for your board. To list available images::

     ls -lh /usr/share/u-boot/salute*/
     export IMAGE=/usr/share/u-boot/salutepm/mcom02-salute-el24pm2-r1.0-1.1-om1-r1.2-uboot.img

#. Update U-Boot::

     mcom02-fw-update $IMAGE
